com.fraudpointer.api.models
Class Profile

java.lang.Object
  com.fraudpointer.api.models.Profile

public class Profile
extends java.lang.Object

The Profile used to carry out the Fraud Assessment.

A FraudAssessment carries out Assessment using the rules that belong to a specific Profile. There are might be many Profile configured in your Account, but only one is selected for the FraudAssessment at hand. This is done at run-time using the Profile Selection Rules.
